ume: The Story of a Murderer","original_language":"en"},{"id":6227,"adult":false,"title":"Pizza Colonia","video":false,"overview":"Italian Francesco ( Mario Adorf ) runs a restaurant in Cologne , partnership is the brewer Zach ( Willy Millowitsch ) . Francesco has problems : a \" Godfather\" makes Zach an offer he can not refuse , the wedding between Francesco's daughter and Zach son bursts , and his wife threatened behind his affair to come up with kiosk owner Hilde , which lasts at least 18 or older to ...","genre_ids":[35,80],"popularity":0.2142,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/vkIydWu1VjabovQrUBKge5NBCH2.jpg","release_date":"1991-12-05","vote_average":3,"backdrop_path":"/ihMItiXR2WaGT3QcH2KeUDmZ1iG.jpg","original_title":"Pizza Colonia","original_language":"de"},{"id":6156,"adult":false,"title":"Sehnsucht nach Rimini","video":false,"overview":"After surviving a heart attack, bus company owner Marianne Toeplitz should actually be more concerned about her health than her ailing business. But she only does this after an argument with her daughter Susanne, who wants to merge with the competition. Against all reason, Marianne sets off for Italy with her granddaughter: Teenager Nellie is in love and wants to join her boyfriend in Rimini - where Marianne experienced an unforgettable romance with the charming Giuseppe many years ago. Susanne follows the two runaways and gets closer to her ex-husband again. Marianne also learns that old love never rusts.","genre_ids":[10770,35,10749],"popularity":0.1655,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/xpaEBy4kODMMqvmQ5EmaNMhAwmA.jpg","release_date":"2007-05-11","vote_average":5,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Sehnsucht nach Rimini","original_language":"de"},{"id":5992,"adult":false,"title":"That Can't Shake Our Willi!","video":false,"overview":"Summer in Germany, anno 1970. Italy is the number one destination. As every year, swarms of Teutonic tourists make their way to the Adriatic Sea. Only Willi Hirsekorn from Castrop-Rauxel has so far no plans to break south. That changes, however, as the bitchy neighbor Mizzi Buntje proudly tells of their upcoming holiday in Italy. Willi can not afford this boasting. Shortly determined, the bags are packed, and already rushes Willi in the car with his wife Sieglinde, daughter Lotti and son Kuno the sun.","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.4366,"vote_count":18,"poster_path":"/vNECjYWQGKqu3XRVgYC4LD0h2Tn.jpg","release_date":"1970-11-26","vote_average":5.444,"backdrop_path":"/koHortEXdZGrtQiqIsneTPO8Skz.jpg","original_title":"Das kann doch unsren Willi nicht erschüttern","original_language":"de"},{"id":7011,"adult":false,"title":"Making Contact","video":false,"overview":"A nine year old boy named Joey, who after the tragic death of his father, begins to experience psychic powers such as allowing him to move inanimate objects with his mind, set things on fire, and even communicate with his dead father. However, not everything is good for Joey as his newly gained powers accidentally awake an evil supernatural force that is contained inside the body of an old ventriloquist's dummy that Joey found in an abandoned house. The supernatural Dummy shows similar powers to Joey's, and soon he puts the lives of everyone near Joey in danger as the evil Dummy has dark plans for Joey's special powers.","genre_ids":[878,14,27,12],"popularity":1.6176,"vote_count":60,"poster_path":"/3RM5CqGzcG5f5gnt1vtOoMDFv0t.jpg","release_date":"1985-11-21","vote_average":5.525,"backdrop_path":"/8JRNR4r7a998im5Zqb1DRJtzsjT.jpg","original_title":"Joey","original_language":"de"},{"id":7349,"adult":false,"title":"Freddy and the Millionaire","video":false,"overview":"","genre_ids":[35],"popularity":0.1509,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/dUqaLDSC2UoJLUvuMfoPlR6qz8I.jpg","release_date":"1961-12-16","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Freddy und der Millionär","original_language":"de"},{"id":7985,"adult":false,"title":"Penelope","video":false,"overview":"Forlorn heiress Penelope Wi